dbt Certification Coach
=======================

This repository contains study material derived from the official dbt
documentation (docs.getdbt.com), the dbt Developer Blog, and the dbt
Analytics Engineering Certification study guide, all © dbt Labs.

The files under `raw/` are excerpts of dbt Labs documentation, retained for
study purposes with a `source_url` in each file's frontmatter linking to the
original. The `wiki/` summaries and `quiz/` questions are derivative study
notes. This repository is intended for internal team use; do not redistribute
the dbt-sourced content externally without observing dbt Labs' terms.

